T*
-0.052 Tw
(quality of DACs [3]. Among the most important dynamic performance parameters are spurious-)Tj
T*
-0.059 Tw
(free dynamic range \(SFDR\), inter-modulation distortion \(IMD\), signal-to-noise ratio \(SNR\) and)Tj
T*
